# VMS Roadmap

## Phase 1
- Repository
- Constitution
- Vision
- Architecture
- Logo
- MVP Planning

## Phase 2
- Login
- Interactive Map
- Pin Locations
- Property Records
- Government Rates
- Area Converter
- Valuation Calculator

## Phase 3
- Public Launch

All features free.

## Phase 4

Introduce VMS Pro after the platform has an active community (100+ users).

Pro Features:
- Add/Edit Records
- Professional Calculators
- Area Converter
- Advanced Survey Tools

Public access to maps and records remains free.
